| EuroG = 9/10 (PS2)<ref name="eurorew" /><br />9/10 (Xbox)<ref name="Eurogamer">{{cite web|author=Reed, Kristin.|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/article.php?article_id=3918|title=Silent Hill 2: Inner Fears Review|work=[[Eurogamer]]|publisher=Eurogamer Network|date=2002-10-02|accessdate=2010-05-30|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/6CIQ61bZB|archivedate=2012-11-19}}</ref>
